profile: Barnes Protection Services has been serving the Ottawa community for over 30 years. Our vision is to provide great home and business alarm systems and other services such as video cameras and home automation that our customers can rely on. We also aim to deliver the best customer satisfaction to our clients. Call us today and we will try and determine the best solution for your security needs!
